A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element

1571 <strong>The Best Faucets for Kitchens, Bathrooms, and Laundry Rooms</strong>&nbsp;

1572 </h3>

1573 <p>Faucets are available in a wide variety of styles, finishes, and sizes. Once strictly utilitarian, they add interest to a room. Wondering how many designs there are? We have answers! Sort faucets by function, finish, or type.&nbsp;</p>

1574 <p>The best thing about our faucet inventory is how simple it is to find the right faucet. If you’re working on a DIY project or need a custom design for your kitchen, bathroom, or laundry room, Vevano Home can help.&nbsp;</p>

Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element
